<!-- Page Hero -->
<section class="bg-[#453E18] py-16">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-3">Driving Advice &amp; Articles</h1>
    <p class="text-[#F8F0CB] text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">Useful guides and information about learning to drive in Glasgow</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Blog Posts -->
<section class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">

      <article class="bg-[#FDFBF1] border border-[#F8F0CB] rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/D1912/images/driving-glasgow.jpg" alt="Driving lessons Glasgow" width="190" height="190" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30] mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider">Driving in Glasgow</p>
          <h2 class="font-bold text-[#453E18] text-lg mb-3 leading-snug">Select the Right Provider of Driving Lessons Glasgow</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#8B7C30] leading-relaxed mb-4">Choosing the right driving school in Glasgow can make a real difference to how quickly you progress and how confident you become. There are many schools to choose from, so it pays to know what to look for before you book.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30]">Accelerate Driving Tuition &bull; Glasgow</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-[#FDFBF1] border border-[#F8F0CB] rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/D1912/images/driving-instructor-schools-glasgow.jpg" alt="Driving schools Glasgow" width="190" height="190" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30] mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider">Choosing a School</p>
          <h2 class="font-bold text-[#453E18] text-lg mb-3 leading-snug">Things Not to Do When Choosing Driving Schools Glasgow</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#8B7C30] leading-relaxed mb-4">When looking for driving schools in Glasgow, it is easy to make decisions based on price alone. But there are several common mistakes that learner drivers make when choosing their instructor, and avoiding them could save you time and money.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30]">Accelerate Driving Tuition &bull; Glasgow</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-[#FDFBF1] border border-[#F8F0CB] rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/D1912/images/driving-lessons-glasgow-significance.jpg" alt="Significance of driving lessons" width="190" height="190" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30] mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider">Why Learn to Drive</p>
          <h2 class="font-bold text-[#453E18] text-lg mb-3 leading-snug">The Significance of Driving Schools Glasgow</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#8B7C30] leading-relaxed mb-4">A good driving school does more than just get you through the test. It gives you the skills, knowledge and confidence to be a safe driver for life. Understanding the significance of professional driving tuition can help you appreciate the value of investing in good lessons.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30]">Accelerate Driving Tuition &bull; Glasgow</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-[#FDFBF1] border border-[#F8F0CB] rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/D1912/images/glasgow-driving-lessons-car.jpg" alt="Driving lessons car Glasgow" width="190" height="190" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30] mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider">Practical Tips</p>
          <h2 class="font-bold text-[#453E18] text-lg mb-3 leading-snug">How to Dress When Taking Driving Lessons Glasgow</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#8B7C30] leading-relaxed mb-4">It might seem like a trivial consideration, but what you wear to your driving lessons can actually have an impact on your comfort and safety. Choosing the right footwear in particular is something many learners overlook entirely.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30]">Accelerate Driving Tuition &bull; Glasgow</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="bg-[#FDFBF1] border border-[#F8F0CB] rounded-xl overflow-hidden hover:shadow-md transition-shadow">
        <img src="/D1912/images/glasgow-driving-lessons-glasgow.jpg" alt="Driving in Glasgow" width="190" height="190" class="w-full aspect-video object-cover" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="p-6">
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30] mb-2 uppercase tracking-wider">General Information</p>
          <h2 class="font-bold text-[#453E18] text-lg mb-3 leading-snug">General Information about Driving in Glasgow</h2>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#8B7C30] leading-relaxed mb-4">Glasgow is a vibrant city with a varied road network that includes busy city centre streets, quiet residential areas, dual carriageways and motorway links. Understanding the layout of the city can help learner drivers feel more prepared before they start their lessons.</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-[#8B7C30]">Accelerate Driving Tuition &bull; Glasgow</p>
        </div>
      </article>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
